post_title: Looking for Eddie Collins blank back
post_content: I know where one of them is because I sold it like a moron a handful of years back.  But there is another one that was owned by a board member (though I can't remember who it was) around 10 years ago.  If the owner sees this, please message me.  I'd love to just know where it is if nothing else.  And I'm ready to buy or trade if it happened to be available (longshot I realize).
